{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "15", "m": "05", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "11", "M": "45", "S": "11"}}, "news": [{"title": "Grade-A office absorption rises 5% to 13.5 million sq ft in Q1 2026: Anarock", "para": "Net absorption of Grade A office space across the top seven cities rose five per cent year-on-year to 13.5 million sq ft in Q1 2026, driven by Bengaluru, Hyderabad and Chennai, according to Anarock. Overall vacancy declined to 15.5 per cent from 16.3 per cent a year earlier, while GCCs continued to account for a rising share of office leasing demand.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/office-space-demand-soars-135-million-sq-ft-absorbed-in-q1-2026/131112888?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-168582/131112888.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Urban Vault expects fit-out & facility management business to generate \u20b950 crore revenue in FY27", "para": "Urban Vault anticipates \u20b950 crore revenue from its design, fit-out, and facility management services by FY27, driven by corporate outsourcing trends. The company recently secured a \u20b9100 crore contract and projects over \u20b9200 crore turnover in FY26 with significant year-on-year growth.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/allied-industries/urban-vault-aims-for-50-crore-revenue-in-fit-out-and-facility-management-by-fy27/131112594?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-117790/131112594.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "allied-industries"}, {"title": "Kolkata metro's orange line extension till sector V likely by December 2026", "para": "Kolkata Metro Railway is set to extend its Orange Line services to Sector V by December 2026. Essential viaduct work at the Chingrighata crossing begins this Friday. This will bridge a critical gap, facilitating the much-needed connection between southern suburbs and Sector V. Permissions have been granted for traffic blocks to complete this vital project.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/kolkata-metros-orange-line-extension-to-sector-v-set-for-december-2026-completion/131111897?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-94324/131111897.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}]}